            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-xs px-3 py-1 bg-green-cyber/10 text-green-cyber rounded border border-green-cyber/30">OpenWeather API</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs px-3 py-1 bg-cyan-electric/10 text-cyan-electric rounded border border-cyan-electric/30">JavaScript</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs px-3 py-1 bg-green-cyber/10 text-green-cyber rounded border border-green-cyber/30">CSS</span>
            </div>
            <a href="https://owen23-ux.github.io/WeatherApp/" target="_blank" class="font-mono text-sm text-green-cyber hover:text-cyan-electric transition-colors">
